1. *M*enja se sezona, pa se i moja odjeća mijenja. (The season is changing, so my clothes are changing too).

2. *M*oja obitelj je veoma velika. (My family is very big).

3. *M*oj prijatelj je liječnik. (My friend is a doctor).

4. *M*ama je donijela ukusne kolače iz pekare. (Mom brought tasty cakes from the bakery).

5. *M*oj brat ide u školu svakog dana. (My brother goes to school every day).

6. *M*oj sin želi biti astronaut. (My son wants to be an astronaut).

7. *M*oj omiljeni sport je plivanje. (My favorite sport is swimming).

8. *M*oj tata je profesor na fakultetu. (My dad is a professor at the university).